    <h2 class="thingy"><font color="#d437a2">Here I will be teaching you about some of the most common words used in everyday life, as well as its translation in a bunch of different languages!</font></h2>
    <br>
    <h2><u><font color ="#0763db">How this works is I will select the Top 10 Most Common English Words, and I will translate them into 5 languages: Spanish, Italian, French, German, and Chinese!</font></u></h2>
